DINNER AND OR DANCING: EITHER AND OR...MAYBE BOTH DINNER AT 6:15 AT JESSE'S, HANOVER, NH DANCING AT 8: 15 AT SALT HILL IN LEBANON, NH

 

COME AND JOIN ME FOR GREAT CONVERSATION... ATMOSPHERE AT JESSE'S AND AT SALT HILL PUB... Salt Hill 's ecoustics are great for conversation too..

Even if you only want coffee and company at Salt Hill.. Its a great place to wine down from the weekend. Come and join me for both or either... Janet M56
